<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <title>NEXTERS RECRUIT Detail</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link href="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link href="/css/detail.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h3>{{role}} detail</h3>
    <nav aria-label="navigation">
        <ul class="pagination">
            <li class="page-item">
                <a class="page-link" href="/{{role}}/{{preRowId}}" aria-label="이전 지원자">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="/list/{{role}}">지원자 목록</a></li>
            <li class="page-item">
                <a class="page-link" href="/{{role}}/{{nextRowId}}" aria-label="다음 지원자">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    {{#resumeDesign}}
        <div class="card">
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item"><b>{{name}}</b></li>
                <li class="list-group-item">{{rowId}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">{{timestamp}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">{{email}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">{{phoneNumber}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">{{question1}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">주분야 : {{question2}}</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">희망분야 : {{question2_2}}</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h5 class="card-header">3. 넥스터즈에 지원하는 이유에 대해 설명해주세요.(300자 제한)</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">{{question3}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h5 class="card-header">4. 자신의 강점 한 가지를 포함해 자유롭게 자기소개를 해주세요. (300자 제한)</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">{{question4}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h5 class="card-header">5. 팀으로 작업하며 문제에 부딪힌 경험과 그 갈등을 어떻게 해결했는지 설명해주세요. (500자 제한)</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">{{question5}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h5 class="card-header">6. 자신의 주요 분야와 관련된 대표적인 프로젝트 경험을 적어주세요. (500자 제한)</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">{{question6}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h5 class="card-header">7. 개인 포트폴리오를 첨부해주세요. (최대 20MB제한 / PDF로 제출)</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text">
                    <a href="{{portfolioLink}}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-link" role="button" aria-pressed="true">{{portfolioLink}}</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    {{/resumeDesign}}
</div>
</body>
</html>